INSERT INTO `product` VALUES ('402881882bbdfe19012bbe0f12880002','2010-10-18 14:38:00','2010-10-28 10:54:28','<p>品名:竹纤维金属腰平角内裤<br />品牌:百武西（BIOLIVING）<br />成分: 95%竹纤维,5%氨纶<br />颜色:黑，灰<br />款式: 男款</p>\r\n<p><br />&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: medium; color: #000000;\"><img src=\"http://image.shopxx.cn/upload/image/201010/9404e02d4c464b9f87f13c130a2ca267.png\" alt=\"\" />&nbsp;<img src=\"http://image.shopxx.cn/upload/image/201010/daabe988632841778db8f569083448ef.png\" alt=\"\" /></span></strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;百武西竹纤维内衣，它杜绝了产品中的重金属和有害化学残留物,避免了长期使用传统产品对肌肤的危害!<br />引领了国际范围内高端肌肤接触品的无添加潮流!它提倡的是舒适健康时尚理念！</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><img src=\"http://image.shopxx.cn/upload/image/201010/0516825ab59b4235beee212960fe44f3.png\" alt=\"\" /></span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">&nbsp;</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><img src=\"http://image.shopxx.cn/upload/image/201010/c2727c37975640c1bd1bf041f4b6dd65.png\" alt=\"\" /></span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">&nbsp;</span></strong></span><span style=\"font-size: medium; color: #99cc00;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p>每日繁忙的背后，总离不开她的细心呵护</p>\r\n<p>贴身衣物只有穿着舒服才会有好的心情</p>\r\n<p>竹纤维系列内衣</p>\r\n<p>舒适、保暖、时尚</p>\r\n<p>而且是会呼吸的内衣哦</p>\r\n<p>清新自然，给您贴身的温暖</p>\r\n<p>出口日韩第一的百武西BIOLIVING无添加纯生态！在自然界可降解！完全无化学添加。</p>\r\n<p>天然抗菌,抑臭,透气,保健！吸湿透气,丝柔亲肤、全身舒爽！</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium; color: #99cc00;\"><img src=\"http://image.shopxx.cn/upload/image/201010/53debfd54eb54b5e80f757677b542e80.png\" alt=\"\" /></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium; color: #99cc00;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium; color: #99cc00;\"><img src=\"http://image.shopxx.cn/upload/image/201010/a5b9b39f5b8d4f299bc97f273132ced0.png\" alt=\"\" /></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium; color: #99cc00;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p>产品特色<br />- 天然抗菌性，有效防止细菌性皮肤病；<br />- 自动调节温度和湿度，明显减轻皮肤由于干燥所产生的干裂、掉皮现象和皮肤瘙痒；<br />- 无重金属,无有害化学物质,无化学直接染色,无农药残留；<br />- 完全天然取材,可自然降解，自然环保，是国际提倡的生态纺织用品；<br />- 吸汗透气、减少静电产生；<br />- 时尚金属感宽边腰带设计，更具时尚感。</p>\r\n<p>保养、水洗说明</p>\r\n<p>1.避免长时间浸泡（超过12小时）；<br />2.不宜大力搓扯、拧干，轻揉拧干即可；<br />3.尽量避免阳光暴晒及烘干，自然风干即可；<br />4.不宜较长时间（超过3小时）接触或使用超过40℃热水清洗；<br />5.避免尖锐物和指甲勾挑产品，用洗衣机清洗应放置于专门的洗衣袋内；<br />6.洗涤时不可氯漂，也不需要加入柔顺剂，用一般碱性的洗涤用品即可。</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium; color: #0000ff;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium; color: #0000ff;\"><img src=\"http://image.shopxx.cn/upload/image/201010/729e98b63d6e4f94b66b25c1ffe44a98.png\" alt=\"\" /></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium; color: #0000ff;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium; color: #0000ff;\"><img src=\"http://image.shopxx.cn/upload/image/201010/d5a12d8e8e294fc2a020738aef880ca4.png\" alt=\"\" /></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium; color: #0000ff;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium; color: #0000ff;\"><img src=\"http://image.shopxx.cn/upload/image/201010/170b5e9b3af149539932bd5f2423ed72.png\" alt=\"\" /></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium; color: #0000ff;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium; color: #0000ff;\"><img src=\"http://image.shopxx.cn/upload/image/201010/19cf33102e6349ef9eb0b46aeedcc9c6.png\" alt=\"\" /></span></p>',2,'/html/product_content/201010/d1692a20d3e0414dbfca30e4088941f2.html',b'0',b'0',b'1',b'0',55,'竹纤维男式内裤 平角内裤 透气抗菌','','竹纤维男式内裤 平角内裤 透气抗菌',0,36,'[{\"bigProductImagePath\":\"/upload/image/201010/bb368776ecd24fa8938f1526b2eb66db_big.jpg\",\"id\":\"bb368776ecd24fa8938f1526b2eb66db\",\"smallProductImagePath\":\"/upload/image/201010/bb368776ecd24fa8938f1526b2eb66db_small.jpg\",\"sourceProductImagePath\":\"/upload/image/201010/bb368776ecd24fa8938f1526b2eb66db.png\",\"thumbnailProduct